metadata.name: Tomorrow #1
metadata.description:
Tomorrow is a particular and emotional series of images created in a really hot summer in Spain. The images took few months to finish but it might be one of the collections I am more proud of.

It does not matter how hot it was Anyon, the model could handle everything including walking barefoot in the desert

3840 × 5760 - 11 MB

Paula Latimori is a photographer and filmmaker whose work explores photography through colors, textures and emotion.

Her work aims to blur the lines between a story where fantasy enters with a simple and natural point of view.

Her personal projects usually mix a very creative and artistic perspective with a very fresh and modern eye.
